# uncast

An utility to uncast an array

## Install

Install the [package](https://npmjs.org/package/uncast) with [npm](http://npmjs.org):

```sh
$ npm install uncast
```

## Usage

```js
const uncast = require('uncast');
let arr1 = [555];
let newInt = uncast(arr1);
//newInt === 555

let arr2 = [1,2,3,4];
let arr3 = uncast(arr2);
//arr3 = [1,2,3,4]

```
